channel.title: Makescents.tv
channel.itunes:author: Tegan Winkfield
channel.description:
Hi Everyone!
I'm thrilled to welcome all of you to my show! I have been working hard all summer to get this up and running. I am so excited that it's finally a reality!
MakesCents.TV is a TV show about discovering what makes "cents" in our daily lives. We'll be exploring lots of things, ranging from regular household items, to vehicles to vacations!
But we also want to know what you think, too! Go to Your Turn, send us a video or an e-postcard about something you've bought or experienced that you've enjoyed - or didn't, and tell the world!
Keep up with new episodes by becoming a fan on www.makescents.tv, Facebook, following me on Twitter, and also by clicking the RSS feed. We're also on You Tube, ITunes and Mevio. There's a variety of different ways to keep in touch - so just pick the one that MakesCents to you and stick to it!
channel.itunes:subtitle: MakesCents.TV is a daily show about discovering what really makes 'cents' in today's world!
